EUROPE BY WEDNESDAY AFTERNOON DECLINING TO 1023. ISOL GALES ACROSS FAIR
ISLE AT FIRST EASING OVERNIGHT. MEANWHILE GALES ACROSS HEBRIDES BAILEY
